name: MySQL5

getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.customCond: ( ( t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 22  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 23  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 24  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 25  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 26  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 27  OR  t1.`DAY_NUMBER` = 28 ) )
getPSDEDataQueryCodeConds.name: 查询条件

queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`CREATE_DATE`,
t1.`CREATE_UID`,
t1.`DAY_NUMBER`,
t1.`ID`,
t1.`NAME`,
t1.`RULE_ID`,
t1.`SHIFT_ID`,
t1.`WRITE_DATE`,
t1.`WRITE_UID`
FROM `ATTENDANCE_WORKDAY` t1
